an-lines in the input scan to the same result."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, this stronger condition can lead to missed barcodes (lower recall)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Confirmation is avoided for barcode types, which are by design resistant to false positives, (e.g. Code128) to maximize recall."}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkonedconfirmationmode","title":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKOneDConfirmationMode","kind":"identifier"}]}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKUpcEanExtensionBehavior\/title","value":"SBSDKUpcEanExtensionBehavior"},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKUpcEanExtensionBehavior\/fragments","value":[{"text":"SBSDKUpcEanExtensionBehavior","kind":"identifier"}]},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKUpcEanExtensionBehavior\/navigatorTitle","value":[{"text":"SBSDKUpcEanExtensionBehavior","kind":"identifier"}]},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBarcodeFormatUpcEanConfiguration\/title","value":"SBSDKBarcodeFormatUpcEanConfiguration"},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBarcodeFormatUpcEanConfiguration\/fragments","value":[{"text":"SBSDK